{"tid":2399882,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美YouTuber拍片假裝持刀搶劫 路人誤以為真拔槍擊斃","createTime":"2021-02-08T13:07:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T15:50:23.000Z","uid":202966,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ec2a977f0f5d86c6926b1904a032dccd454a688e","tid":2399882,"uid":202966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:07:27.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國田納西州納什維爾當地時間5日晚間9時25分許，警方接獲槍擊案通報連忙到場了解，原來是YouTuber為了要拍惡作劇影片假裝持刀搶劫，怎知路人以為真有歹徒連忙拔槍將其擊斃。<br />\n<br />\n據《美聯社》報導，目擊者透露，20歲男子威爾克斯（Timothy Wilks）當時和朋友手持屠宰刀，在停車場接近包括斯塔恩斯（David Starnes Jr.）在內的一群人，想要拍攝惡作劇搶劫影片再上傳到YouTube。<br />\n<br />\n斯塔恩斯並不知道這是惡作劇，看到持刀劫匪來襲趕緊拿槍射殺對方，以便保護自己和好友們。納什維爾警方表示，目前全案仍在調查當中，尚未有人因這起槍擊案而被指控任何罪嫌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3435209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3435209&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUisls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=0e19a3a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3435209&h=58c4c97b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3435209</a>"},{"pid":"5d86e4c81c5b711c75ae09b77bc947174dc4701f","tid":2399882,"uid":251477,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:12:07.000Z","msg":"大J原來有玩原神 唔知佢有冇課金<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2382698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2382698</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n樓主係咪諗住屈完人唔道歉改個名當冇事？"},{"pid":"62adbf44d10b6b1ed84ed2a0a69f4c3722a23dec","tid":2399882,"uid":130402,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:14:28.000Z","msg":"大J原來有玩原神 唔知佢有冇課金<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2382698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2382698</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n樓主條撚樣無證無據屈鳩完人，道歉都無句想不停出post洗底"},{"pid":"89edcd37c9fe592f726d82fb15dfb59960cb66db","tid":2399882,"uid":205043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"